content.comment:
We updated the paper to address some of the reviewers' comments. The major changes include the following.

1. Clarified that our goal with this work is to develop time representation methods rather than a new RNN model. Our methods can enhance existing RNN models to deal with continuous time;
2. Added more experimental results, including statistical significance for the performance with three public datasets;
3. Updated Figure 3 for the performance with the three public datasets resulted from better tuning;
4. Added Figure 4 to discuss learned time representation.

